Package: triangdist
Title: Triangular Distribution Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(Lorena, Cortijo, Capel, locorca@alumni.uv.es, role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package providing the core distribution functions for the 
    triangular distribution: density (dtriang), cumulative distribution 
    (ptriang), quantile function (qtriang), and random generation (rtriang).
